          Inspecting leather tags and style numbers
      </h3>
      <p class="body-text">
        The leather tag on a Balenciaga bag contains crucial information that can help with style verification and verify its authenticity. The style number on the tag should match the bag’s design. An authentic Balenciaga bag will have matching style numbers on both the front and back of the tag. 
        <br><br>
        Additionally, the evolution of font styles and labels over the years can provide valuable clues about the bag’s authenticity. By carefully inspecting these details, you can ensure that you’re investing in a genuine Balenciaga bag.
      </p>
